llows you to browse the contrarius website in future without being shown our cookie notice do third parties use cookies on the contrarius website no can a website user block cookies any user of the contrarius website can block cookies you may do so by adjusting your browser settings if you do disable our cookies you may find that a large proportion of the site will not be accessible more information if you require any further information about the contrarius cookie policy please contact us at clientservicecontrariuscom close × legal statement please read the legal statement and terms of use carefully your use of our website and email services is subject to your acceptance of and compliance with our terms and conditions by using our website you agree and accept all of our terms and conditions if you do not wish to be bound by these terms and conditions please do not access this website legal statement the information contained on our website and email services is being made available for the benefit of the present investors in the contrarius icav and its subfunds the contrarius global equity fund and the contrarius global absolute fund collectively referred to as “the funds” and such other persons expressly authorised by the funds to receive such information provided that such investors and other persons are not prohibited under the applicable laws of their citizenship domicile or residence from receiving such information no other persons are authorised by the funds to receive such information the funds are made available by prospectus or other forms of disclosure statements specified by applicable law only each funds prospectusdisclosure statement contains important information which you should read carefully before investing notice of nonsolicitation the information contained on our website is not intended to constitute an offer or solicitation of any securities to any person and is not intended for distribution to anyone in any jurisdiction where such distribution